Plot

三種方法視覺化呈現資料：Base Plotting System、Lattice、ggplot2

Base Plotting System

用R內建空氣品質的資料集airquality來練習

library(datasets)
head(airquality)
##   Ozone Solar.R Wind Temp Month Day
## 1    41     190  7.4   67     5   1
## 2    36     118  8.0   72     5   2
## 3    12     149 12.6   74     5   3
## 4    18     313 11.5   62     5   4
## 5    NA      NA 14.3   56     5   5
## 6    28      NA 14.9   66     5   6

畫直方圖(Histogram) 圖名字Histogram of Month，x軸名字月份，y軸名字頻率

hist(x=airquality$Month, 
     main="Histogram of Month",         
     xlab="Month",                      
     ylab="Frequency")

畫盒鬚圖(Box Plot) 看不同月份Ozone數值的分布情況

boxplot(formula = Ozone ~ Month, 
        data = airquality,       
        xlab = "Month",          
        ylab = "Ozone (ppb)",    
        col ="gray")

散布圖(Scatter Plot) 看月份(Month)和氣溫(Temp)之間的關係

plot(x=airquality$Month,            
     y=airquality$Temp,             
     main="Month to Temperature",   
     xlab="Month(1~12)",            
     ylab="Temperature(degrees F)")

臭氧與風的散布關係圖

plot(x=airquality$Ozone,
     y=airquality$Wind,
     main="Ozone to Wind",
     xlab="Ozone(ppb)",
     ylab="Wind(mph)",
     pch=16                  
)

找出五月與八月的資料，標上藍色與紅色的點 在右上角加入圖標 建立一個線性回歸 畫上回歸的趨勢線

May_data <- airquality[airquality$Month==5, ] 
Aug_data <- airquality[airquality$Month==8, ] 

plot(x=airquality$Ozone,
     y=airquality$Wind,
     main="Ozone to Wind",
     xlab="Ozone(ppb)",
     ylab="Wind(mph)",
     pch=16                  
) 
points(x=May_data$Ozone,                       
       y=May_data$Wind, 
       pch=16,                 
       col="blue") 

points(x=Aug_data$Ozone, 
       y=Aug_data$Wind, 
       pch=16,               
       col="red")

legend("topright",                                
       pch = 1,                                   
       col = c("blue", "red", "black"),            
       legend = c("May", "August", "Other Month") 
       )

lm.model <- lm(Wind~Ozone, airquality)
 
abline(lm.model,lwd=5)

Lattice

載入lattice

library(lattice)

在Lattice中，畫直方圖(Histogram)

airquality$Month <- as.factor(airquality$Month) 

histogram(x= ~ Ozone | Month,  
          data=airquality,     
          xlab="Ozone(ppb)",  
          layout=c(5,1))

畫盒鬚圖(Box Plot)

bwplot(x = Ozone ~ Month,      
       data = airquality,     
       xlab =          
       )

機率密度圖

densityplot( ~ Ozone ,      
            data=airquality
            )

畫3D圖

cloud(x=Wind~Temp+Ozone | Month, 
       data=airquality         
      )

畫散布圖

xyplot(x=Wind~Temp,         
       data=airquality,     
       group = Month,       
       
       auto.key=list(space="top",          
                     columns=5,           
                     title="Month Labels",
                     cex.title=1)         
       )

ggplot2

library(ggplot2)

histogram

qplot(x=Ozone,                      
      data=airquality,              
      geom="histogram",             
      main = "Histogram of Ozone",  
      xlab="Ozone(ppb)",            
      binwidth = 25,                
      fill= Month                  
      )
## Warning: Removed 37 rows containing non-finite values (stat_bin).

散布圖

qplot(x=Temp,                               
      y=Ozone,                              
      data=airquality,                      
      geom="point",                         
      main = "Scatter Plot of Ozone-Temp",  
      xlab="Temp",                          
      ylab="Ozone(ppb)",                    
      color= Month                          
      )

qplot(x=Temp,                             
      data=airquality,                     
      geom="density",

      color= Month           
)

qplot(x=Month,                               
      y=Ozone,

)
